Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　劫持巴士的恐怖分子的要求是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　他們要求立即撤出駐在阿爾泰的維和部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:16.64,Note3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}艾亞利茲行政府　赫其薩貢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及釋放為接受審判而關押在我國Desperate監獄的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那基·泰·阿爾泰前大公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波曼准將　報告情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Madam！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被佔據的是往返於東部國境與首都之間的長途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人質連同乘務員在內共十名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子們在車內設置了炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅說要求得不到滿足的話就引爆炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下　總統選舉迫在眼前的這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對應失誤的話選情的前景將不容樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是警察在處理麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12分鐘之前　我們國家安全保障局已接過了指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DELTA-乙HiME部隊已經在現場就位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據閣下的命令　任何時候都能突入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然對方手上有人質
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就不可輕易出手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對應要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰名為「Silent Sea」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「寂靜的大海」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過獎了　閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請一定靜靜地去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的　已經像平常那樣派人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她逃了~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是已經說過那種大小的石頭已經沒效了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-1　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-2　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-3　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Target in sight　任何時候都能射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待機　多蘿茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須避免給對方造成不必要的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平靜地　冷靜地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Silent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:29.24,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(475,10)}第二幕　暴·風·雨的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了　波曼准將
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准將由我們這邊安靜地 秘密地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我釋放人質　堂堂正正地決一勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准將！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿米特吉准將！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准將！好好教訓一下那些恐怖分子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈拉德隊長　表演個節目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好　冷靜　冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子已經遲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦　伊莉娜·伍茲?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　聽得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西還真方便吶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?　愛莉卡·夢宮果然是在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車型呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了　膽小鬼　快回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個大嗓門的女人是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Meister遙·阿米特吉　克利桑德的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個破壞的阿米特吉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步走錯後果可是不堪設想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白　那是我的饅頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臨時中斷與石上候選人的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士劫持事件似乎有新的動態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攝影機轉向那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出來的話我這邊就要動手了　你們這群惡黨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來！過來的話我就把乘客全部炸死！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種試試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有艾亞利茲之魂的人才不會被炸彈什麼的炸死呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是從加爾德羅貝趕來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責指揮的是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?　是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為DELTA的隊長可是失職了呢　千繪·哈拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些非正式的話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓神山消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連真白女王和Meister舞衣都…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧　我不是說過了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦　你認識Meister舞衣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然認識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個開拉麵店的女孩子吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說想開連鎖店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就叫她本店設在艾亞利茲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經給了她忠告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有　在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了要去搜尋真白陛下的字條
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister愛莉卡也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後的追蹤呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　已經找到了她所乘坐的長途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能解決嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點　我會幫你們一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人的來歷已經查明了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被認定是主謀者的人確實是原阿爾泰的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出身於陸軍近衛師團的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現場狀況怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被准將大鬧一場以後　現在陷入了膠著狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風花市事件的情報還錯綜複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰略乙HiME限制交涉也近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允許失敗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人　要鬆餅嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛還這麼鎮靜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就是束手無策吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破這種狀況不就是我們的工作嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說強行突破什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請鎮靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算放著不管　事態也總會有變化的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說不穿舞斗服就強行突破也太那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薩拉·加拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要履行乙HiME的義務　跟舞斗服什麼的沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好~好~　是氣勢吧　氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佔據巴士的恐怖分子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下屆總統最合適的人選
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石上　石上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了大家的希望　期待的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亙·石上來傾聽各位的要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰放那個傢伙過去的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位恐怖分子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊你這瘋女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亙·石上　總算見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在電視上狂批雪之和我的就是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不會明白那是為什麼的　遙·阿米特吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位國民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此粗野又暴力的人居然進入國政的中樞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你更讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克利桑德和阿米特吉是艾亞利茲的智慧和靈魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾下去　奇怪的帽子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要囉哩八嗦了　我們做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火大!　才不呢　那種事情是我做的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道為什麼我能忍受如此的侮辱嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道為什麼嗎　遙·阿米特吉?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為交了女朋友啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯　正因為有愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能突破重重困難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後　我會為了愛肅清這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這份洋溢的感情　要向艾亞利茲全體國民…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這人誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前好像是個畫人像的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　在全世界前介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的秘書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久將成為這個國家的第一夫人的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Sweet Honey 鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是這邊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真礙事　受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是煩這種蠢男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友繪·瑪格麗特?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識這個傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瓦爾基裡部隊的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為好玩而出賣自己人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大壞蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴　你們這群垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一夫人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大錯特錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親手解決了石上的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是新的總統候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友繪君　收手吧　看上去真讓人痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧　請給我投下純潔的一票　接受我的支配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要自己在那大吵大鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不給我認真談判的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把這傢伙的腦袋轟碎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾亞利茲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇　准將　千繪前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不要察覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多麼幸運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我放棄做家務而出來是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說　搶巴士的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看看這個奇特的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是…瞧　就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「星滅者」的愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那麼了不起的事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還沒明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛莉卡　給我收拾掉這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的喲~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白不在　我現在沒辦法使用乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次請你做我們的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人…人質是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的孩子怎麼這麼傻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛睡醒時誰都是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情真好　愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的我回家看電視了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是友繪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾亞利茲共和國總統　雪之·克利桑德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我親自來和你們交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　乘上巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話我就聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換　我要求你們釋放人質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多事情就拜託了呢　准將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把她也放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說她是大公殿下最大的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾亞利茲決不會屈服於恐怖主義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且　連風花王國都會變成你們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶說過　打女人的男人是最差勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧　雪之小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝　愛莉卡也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我無論如何都想自己去找到真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小遙不見的話　我想我也會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是我不是總統的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之小姐和准將從來不吵架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我和小遙之間有個規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,規矩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對　要是我做錯的話小遙會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小遙做錯的話　我會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後兩個人好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到兩人都覺得正確的道路時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就毫不猶豫地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃五柱之一　銀河的藍玉　薩拉·加拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請求備用系統給予認證
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.79,Note3,NTP,0,0,0,,Surrogate System
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:53.63,Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小遙一定會做我認為是正確的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的乙HiME　遙·阿米特吉准將
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了　雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵襲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐　怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎戰　快開火　開火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綁架人質　威脅我們釋放那基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借助別人力量的你們　從一開始就沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要報仇的話　就用自己的雙手　堂堂正正地去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是子獸?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.67,Note3,NTP,0,0,0,,CHILD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對像認定為敵對性生命體！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DELTA Force　迎戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准將！雪之小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙·阿米特吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持有珠洲之黃玉的吾之乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以吾之名　解放汝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下　准將
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以總統之名　把你打成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快去避難　克利桑德閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你　Meister薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人　你看到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…不　那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真祖大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白的金剛石　Grand Meister　二三·姬野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DELTA　Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真祖怎麼可能會襲擊我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我來揭露你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要抱到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要追得太深
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Luck！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞背後襲擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就交給你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准將…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准將…准將！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:48.46,Note4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}艾亞利茲境內　Desperate監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾呢　被釋放的機會溜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~那群人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算跟那些劫持巴士的人走　也很快就會被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況最後失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無可救藥的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請說我聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日三餐還能午睡　我挺喜歡這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用像在黑之谷那樣被強制勞動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說　黑之谷裡發生什麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對　黑之谷消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白和舞衣也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我　那基先生　大家在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就是說「他」來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　該說是「她」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被幹掉的乙HiME們的納米機器發生硬化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有生命反應　身體卻硬得像礦石一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的只是很少的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記載在我從阿爾泰的遺跡裡找到的文獻裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:16.39,Note4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,450)}{\1c&HC9CAC8&}阿爾泰公國　黑曜宮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:28.75,Note4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}{\1c&HC9CAC8&}（俗稱）　條紋亭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在條紋團的根據地辦Meister學校真的好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你還說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城裡的大官們有事的話讓他們來這裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算Peace Maker也和一般的小混混沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜託你的那個東西呢　小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真打算要去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從回到這裡以後我就很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這麼冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的東西都那麼油膩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為討厭這裡才去了加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被降職了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的發洩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛~雖然我不是很贊成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽傳聞說你們五柱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管閒事　小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister朱麗葉特·奈緒·張
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把客人帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了　奈緒前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:26:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS}{\fs76}{\3c&HAB45BC&}縞之舞{\3c&HD35765&}/少女的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:50.05,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(350,300)\move(280,190,480,190)}{\1c&H13EEFA&}{\3c&H1D88D9&\bord3\be1}老虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.06,0:25:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　找我有什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.22,0:25:50.05,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(400,280,300,280)}{\1c&H13EEFA&}{\3c&H1D88D9&\bord3\be1}你要成為老虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.30,0:25:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來做下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.37,0:25:52.81,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(510,280,510,150)\fn@Arial Unicode MS\frz-90}{\1c&H0393AF&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1}{\bord8\t(0,300,\bord3)}最強！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.66,0:25:52.81,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(250,150,250,230)\fn@Arial Unicode MS\frz-90}{\1c&H0393AF&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\be1}賭上最後的舞斗服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.10,0:25:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就為這種事情把我叫來嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.60,0:25:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.67,0:25:55.25,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\fn@Arial Unicode MS\frz-90}{\1c&H864EBD&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs25\t(\fs80)}乙HiME們的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.40,0:25:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薩拉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們根本不懂什麼是下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.01,0:25:57.82,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\fad(300,300)\move(480,220,380,280)}{\1c&H13EEFA&}{\3c&H1D88D9&}熾熱的戰鬥即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.01,0:25:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來給你們做示範
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.60,0:26:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到的話就做做看啊
